OL,3,CPSNI chief prepared to mount court
OL,4,Cchallenge to secure pay rise for
OL,5,Cofficers
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland's police chief has
OL,8,Fsaid he is prepared to go to court to
OL,9,Fsecure a pay rise for his officers as
OL,10,Fhe warned that the PSNI's finances are
OL,11,Fthe worst they have ever been.
OL,13,FJon Boutcher said he was "calling
OL,14,Ftime" on the continuing "dilution" of
OL,15,Fpolicing capabilities in Northern
OL,16,FIreland as he confirmed an intent to
OL,17,Frecruit 350 new officers in the coming
OL,18,Ffinancial year, 100 of them between
OL,19,FApril and July.
