OL,5,Cofficers
OL,7,FThe chief constable has been lobbying
OL,8,FStormont officials and the UK
OL,9,FGovernment to secure the estimated #20
OL,10,Fmillion required for the Pay Review
OL,11,FBoard-recommended 7% rise for the
OL,12,Fexisting workforce.
OL,14,FLast year Mr Boutcher raised the
OL,15,Fprospect of him introducing a pay rise
OL,16,Ffor his officers without securing the
OL,17,Fmoney to fund it.
