OL,3,CPSNI chief prepared to mount court
OL,4,Cchallenge to secure pay rise for
OL,5,Cofficers
OL,7,FAt the time, he acknowledged that such
OL,8,Fa step could prompt a formal sanction
OL,9,Ffor breaching his responsibilities as
OL,10,Fan accounting officer for the PSNI's
OL,11,Fbudget.
OL,13,FOn Thursday he told members of his
OL,14,Foversight body ` the Northern Ireland
OL,15,FPolicing Board ` that he was exploring
OL,16,Foptions around mounting a legal
OL,17,Fchallenge to secure the funding
OL,18,Frequired.
