OL,5,Cofficers
OL,7,FHe expressed hope that course of
OL,8,Faction would not be needed and that a
OL,9,Frestored Stormont executive would move
OL,10,Fto divert more funds to the PSNI.
OL,12,FOn the issue of the stalled pay rise,
OL,13,Fhe told board members: "I'm exploring
OL,14,Fthe legal opportunities that might be
OL,15,Favailable to me. I'm very conscious
OL,16,Fthat courts have always been nervous
OL,17,Fabout making judgments with regards to
OL,18,Fallocations of spend with regards to
OL,19,Fpublic services.
