OL,7,F"But I have statutory duties within
OL,8,Fthe organisation to keep people safe,
OL,9,Fto safeguard vulnerable groups, as
OL,10,Fwell as an accounting officer function.
OL,12,F"And that prospect is one that I have
OL,13,Fnot put to one side with regards to
OL,14,Fmaking sure that these issues are
OL,15,Feffectively discussed in a format
OL,16,Fwhere proper and more informed
OL,17,Fdecisions could be made around funding
OL,18,Ffor the PSNI."
