OL,7,FMr Boutcher added: "At the moment
OL,8,Fthere has been a dilution, a reduction
OL,9,Fin our police capabilities over time,
OL,10,Fwe haven't kept pace.
OL,12,F"And that's something to do I think
OL,13,Fwith how we have, or have not, managed
OL,14,Fto get the allocation of budget that
OL,15,Fwe need. So, I'm calling time on that.
