OL,3,CPSNI chief prepared to mount court
OL,4,Cchallenge to secure pay rise for
OL,5,Cofficers
OL,7,F"We've got to get the funding that
OL,8,Fthis organisation needs. I would just
OL,9,Fsay once more because it's important I
OL,10,Fthink for the organisation to know my
OL,11,Fposition on this ` I am determined to
OL,12,Fpay them that pay award. I'm
OL,13,Fdetermined. I will go to court over
OL,14,Fit. I might lose. I might lose, but
OL,15,Fthey deserve that money.
OL,17,F"I'm hoping now recent events mean I
OL,18,Fwon't have to do that, because that's
OL,19,Fnot in the interest of anybody or
OL,20,Fpublic money. But something has to
OL,21,Fgive here."
