OL,7,FCommenting on the PSNI's current
OL,8,Fbudget shortfall, he added: "It is the
OL,9,Fworst financial position this
OL,10,Forganisation's ever been in."
OL,12,FWhile the PSNI has a recommended
OL,13,Fofficer headcount of 7,500, the actual
OL,14,Fnumber of serving officers is
OL,15,Fcurrently below 6,500.
OL,17,FMr Boutcher said the organisation
OL,18,Factually needed around 8,000 officers
OL,19,Fto perform all the duties expected of
OL,20,Fit.
