OL,5,Cofficers
OL,7,F"Many officers are saying that they
OL,8,Fsimply can't afford to be part of the
OL,9,FPSNI, officers and staff," he said.
OL,11,F"We have around about 600 people
OL,12,Fleaving the organisation each year,
OL,13,Faround about 350 of those are police
OL,14,Fofficers.
OL,16,F"The recruitment that we're going to
OL,17,Fdo is seeking to retain the headcount
OL,18,Fthat we're currently at.
